<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>《中暑》电子场刊</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;600;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap');

:root {
  --bg-paper: #E8E4E0;
  --bg-warm: #F0EBE5;
  --red-spiral: #8B2323;
  --red-dark: #6B1A1A;
  --yellow-text: #C4951A;
  --yellow-bright: #D4A017;
  --gray-text: #4A4540;
  --gray-light: #8A8580;
  --gray-shadow: #B5B0A8;
  --black-ink: #2A2520;
  --white-pure: #FAF8F5;
}

* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

html { scroll-snap-type: y mandatory; }

body {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg-paper);
  color: var(--gray-text);
  overflow-x: hidden;
}

.programme {
  max-width: 480px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.page {
  min-height: 100vh;
  min-height: 100dvh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 48px 32px;
  position: relative;
  scroll-snap-align: start;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* ===== P1 COVER ===== */
.cover-page {
  background: var(--bg-paper);
}

.spiral-bg {
  position: absolute;
  top: -60px;
  right: -80px;
  width: 320px;
  height: 320px;
  opacity: 0.1;
  pointer-events: none;
  animation: spiralPulse 10s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes spiralPulse {
  0%, 100% { transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg); }
  50% { transform: scale(1.08) rotate(8deg); }
}

.spiral-bg svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }

.cover-tag {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 8px;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.cover-title {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 80px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--yellow-text);
  line-height: 1;
  letter-spacing: 12px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}

.cover-title .char-1 { display: inline-block; animation: charFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite; }
.cover-title .char-2 { display: inline-block; animation: charFloat 4s ease-in-out 0.6s infinite; }

@keyframes charFloat {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50% { transform: translateY(-6px); }
}

.cover-subtitle {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  margin-top: 24px;
  letter-spacing: 4px;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.cover-author {
  margin-top: 56px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--gray-light);
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}

.cover-scroll {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 40px;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--gray-light);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  animation: bounceDown 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
}

@keyframes bounceDown {
  0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.4; }
  50% { transform: translateY(10px); opacity: 0.8; }
}

/* ===== P2 CONCEPT ===== */
.concept-page {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-paper) 0%, var(--bg-warm) 100%);
}

.brush-stroke {
  position: absolute;
  height: 6px;
  background: var(--red-spiral);
  opacity: 0.06;
  border-radius: 3px;
  transform: rotate(-20deg);
}

.brush-1 { top: 80px; right: 20px; width: 50px; }
.brush-2 { top: 180px; left: 30px; width: 30px; transform: rotate(15deg); }
.brush-3 { bottom: 120px; right: 40px; width: 40px; transform: rotate(-35deg); }

.concept-quote {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  line-height: 2;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 0 16px;
}

.concept-quote .highlight {
  color: var(--yellow-text);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.footprints {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
  opacity: 0.25;
  margin-top: 40px;
}

.footprint {
  width: 8px;
  height: 14px;
  background: var(--gray-shadow);
  border-radius: 50% 50% 40% 40%;
  transform: rotate(-15deg);
  animation: footprintFade 3s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.footprint:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.3s; transform: rotate(15deg) translateY(-4px); }
.footprint:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.6s; transform: rotate(-15deg); }

@keyframes footprintFade {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 0.2; }
  50% { opacity: 0.5; }
}

/* ===== P3 OPENING ===== */
.opening-page {
  background: var(--white-pure);
}

.big-number {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 140px;
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  opacity: 0.06;
  line-height: 1;
  position: absolute;
  top: 40px;
  left: 24px;
}

.opening-text {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  color: var(--black-ink);
  line-height: 1.9;
  text-align: left;
  padding-left: 20px;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--yellow-text);
  max-width: 300px;
}

.opening-detail {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--gray-text);
  line-height: 2.2;
  max-width: 300px;
  margin-top: 32px;
  text-align: left;
}

.opening-detail em {
  color: var(--yellow-text);
  font-style: normal;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.side-label {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--gray-light);
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  margin-top: 32px;
}

/* ===== P4 BURNING ===== */
.burn-page {
  background: var(--white-pure);
}

.stagger-line {
  font-size: 19px;
  color: var(--gray-text);
  line-height: 2.6;
  text-align: left;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 300px;
}

.stagger-line:nth-child(2) { padding-left: 36px; }
.stagger-line:nth-child(3) { padding-left: 72px; }

/* ===== P5 DOCTOR ===== */
.dialogue-page {
  background: var(--bg-paper);
}

.dialogue-block {
  max-width: 320px;
  padding: 0 8px;
}

.dialogue-text {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--black-ink);
  line-height: 2.2;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.dialogue-source {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray-light);
  margin-top: 24px;
  text-align: right;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* ===== P6 LIE ===== */
.lie-page {
  background: var(--white-pure);
}

.highlight-box {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(196,149,26,0.05) 0%, rgba(139,35,35,0.03) 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(139,35,35,0.08);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 40px 28px;
  max-width: 340px;
  text-align: center;
  position: relative;
}

.highlight-box::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  width: 50px;
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--yellow-text);
  border-radius: 0 0 2px 2px;
}

.highlight-box p {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 2;
  color: var(--gray-text);
}

.highlight-box strong {
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ===== P7 MERITOCRACY ===== */
.merit-page {
  background: var(--white-pure);
}

.keyword-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  background: rgba(139,35,35,0.07);
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.merit-text {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 2.4;
  color: var(--gray-text);
  max-width: 300px;
  text-align: left;
}

/* ===== P8 PARENTS ===== */
.parents-page {
  background: var(--bg-paper);
}

.parents-quote {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 26px;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  line-height: 1.8;
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 300px;
}

.parents-quote::before {
  content: '"';
  display: block;
  font-size: 80px;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  opacity: 0.08;
  line-height: 0.6;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.parents-detail {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--gray-text);
  line-height: 2.2;
  max-width: 300px;
  margin-top: 32px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* ===== P9 ROOFTOP ===== */
.rooftop-page {
  background: var(--white-pure);
}

.rooftop-quote {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--black-ink);
  line-height: 2;
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 300px;
}

.rooftop-quote strong {
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* ===== P10 MEET ===== */
.meet-page {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-warm) 0%, var(--bg-paper) 100%);
}

.meet-whisper {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--gray-light);
  font-style: italic;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.meet-dialogue {
  max-width: 320px;
  text-align: center;
}

.meet-dialogue .dialogue-text {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--black-ink);
  line-height: 2;
}

.meet-dialogue .dialogue-source {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

/* ===== P11 GOLD ===== */
.gold-page {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-warm) 0%, var(--bg-paper) 100%);
}

.gold-dialogue {
  max-width: 340px;
  text-align: center;
}

.gold-dialogue .dialogue-text {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 32px;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.gold-dialogue .dialogue-source {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 28px;
  color: var(--yellow-text);
  font-size: 14px;
}

/* ===== P12 ENDING ===== */
.ending-page {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-warm) 0%, var(--bg-paper) 100%);
}

.diamond-divider {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  background: var(--red-spiral);
  opacity: 0.2;
  transform: rotate(45deg);
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.ending-quote {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  line-height: 2;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.ending-question {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: var(--yellow-text);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.ending-title {
  font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--red-spiral);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.ending-lines {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--gray-light);
  line-height: 2.2;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-align: center;
}

/* Responsive */
@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .page { padding: 40px 24px; }
  .cover-title { font-size: 64px; letter-spacing: 8px; }
  .concept-quote { font-size: 20px; }
  .big-number { font-size: 120px; }
  .opening-text { font-size: 20px; }
  .parents-quote { font-size: 22px; }
  .gold-dialogue .dialogue-text { font-size: 28px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="programme">

  <!-- P1: COVER -->
  <section class="page cover-page">
    <div class="spiral-bg">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200">
        <path d="M100,100 m-80,0 a80,80 0 1,0 160,0 a80,80 0 1,0 -160,0" fill="none" stroke="#8B2323" stroke-width="3" opacity="0.3"/>
        <path d="M100,100 m-60,0 a60,60 0 1,0 120,0 a60,60 0 1,0 -120,0" fill="none" stroke="#8B2323" stroke-width="3" opacity="0.4"/>
        <path d="M100,100 m-40,0 a40,40 0 1,0 80,0 a40,40 0 1,0 -80,0" fill="none" stroke="#8B2323" stroke-width="3" opacity="0.5"/>
        <path d="M100,100 m-20,0 a20,20 0 1,0 40,0 a20,20 0 1,0 -40,0" fill="none" stroke="#8B2323" stroke-width="3" opacity="0.6"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="6" fill="#8B2323" opacity="0.7"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-tag">荒诞戏剧</div>
    <h1 class="cover-title">
      <span class="char-1">中</span><span class="char-2">暑</span>
    </h1>
    <div class="cover-subtitle">徐卓 戏剧作品</div>
    <div class="cover-author">HEATSTROKE IN WINTER</div>
    <div class="cover-scroll">&darr; 向上滑动</div>
  </section>

  <!-- P2: CONCEPT -->
  <section class="page concept-page">
    <div class="brush-stroke brush-1"></div>
    <div class="brush-stroke brush-2"></div>
    <div class="brush-stroke brush-3"></div>
    <div class="concept-quote">
      冬天不会中暑&mdash;&mdash;<br>
      这是全世界告诉你的常识。<br>
      但<span class="highlight">你的身体正在燃烧</span>，<br>
      这只有你知道。
    </div>
    <div class="footprints">
      <div class="footprint"></div>
      <div class="footprint"></div>
      <div class="footprint"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P3: OPENING -->
  <section class="page opening-page">
    <div class="big-number">11</div>
    <div class="opening-text">
      穿最正式的衬衫、毛衣、西裤、羽绒服，去第11场面试。
    </div>
    <div class="opening-detail">
      大厅里密密麻麻全是人，全部都在打电话。<br><br>
      太吵了，耳朵找不到一个重点。<br><br>
      好渴，但不能喝水&mdash;&mdash;<em>面试的时候不能上厕所</em>。
    </div>
    <div class="side-label">你告诉自己：忍耐</div>
  </section>

  <!-- P4: BURNING -->
  <section class="page burn-page">
    <div class="stagger-line">可你明明在燃烧。</div>
    <div class="stagger-line">由内而外的热，热到心里发慌，</div>
    <div class="stagger-line">身体像炉子里的饼、开锅的水蒸气。</div>
    <div class="footprints" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="footprint"></div>
      <div class="footprint"></div>
      <div class="footprint"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P5: DOCTOR -->
  <section class="page dialogue-page">
    <div class="dialogue-block">
      <div class="dialogue-text">
        &ldquo;愿意加班，可以单休？&rdquo;<br><br>
        你点了点头。<br><br>
        &ldquo;人一旦自己剥削自己，<br>就真的没救了。&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="dialogue-source">&mdash;&mdash; 医生</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P6: LIE -->
  <section class="page lie-page">
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <p><strong>我们生活在一个巨大的谎言里：</strong><br><br>当下的痛苦可以兑换未来的幸福。<br><br>就像驴子眼前栓住的胡萝卜，<br>始终和驴保持着距离。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P7: MERITOCRACY -->
  <section class="page merit-page">
    <div class="keyword-tag">优绩主义</div>
    <div class="merit-text">
      是一台精密的跑步机&mdash;&mdash;<br><br>
      你以为在奔跑，其实从未移动。<br><br>
      你以隐忍牺牲换取认同，<br>
      在无休止的自我证明中<br>
      放逐了最真实的感知。
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P8: PARENTS -->
  <section class="page parents-page">
    <div class="parents-quote">
      &ldquo;心静自然凉。&rdquo;
    </div>
    <div class="parents-detail">
      父母追上天台，反复拧开那盏小太阳。<br><br>
      你拧掉，他们打开。<br>
      你拧掉，他们打开。<br><br>
      当你面前不是一扇玻璃窗，<br>
      而是两颗爱你的心的时候，<br>
      打碎它们，就变得异常困难。
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P9: ROOFTOP -->
  <section class="page rooftop-page">
    <div class="rooftop-quote">
      <strong>&ldquo;我保证我没有想跳楼，</strong><br><br>
      其实我只是想凉快一下。&rdquo;
    </div>
    <div class="footprints" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="footprint"></div>
      <div class="footprint"></div>
      <div class="footprint"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P10: MEET -->
  <section class="page meet-page">
    <div class="meet-whisper">直到你遇见她 &mdash; 那个麻花辫女孩</div>
    <div class="meet-dialogue">
      <div class="dialogue-text">
        &ldquo;我那个时候&hellip;&hellip;<br>会不会也中暑了？&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="dialogue-source">&mdash;&mdash; 我</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P11: GOLD -->
  <section class="page gold-page">
    <div class="gold-dialogue">
      <div class="dialogue-text">
        &ldquo;我看出来了。&rdquo;
      </div>
      <div class="dialogue-source">&mdash;&mdash; 她</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- P12: ENDING -->
  <section class="page ending-page">
    <div class="diamond-divider"></div>
    <div class="ending-quote">
      原来不止我一个人，<br>
      会在冬天中暑。
    </div>
    <div class="ending-question">你呢？</div>
    <div class="ending-title">《中暑》</div>
    <div class="ending-lines">
      写给每一个在寒冬里灼烧的灵魂<br><br>
      最高的自由，是忠于自我的感知<br>
      真正的治愈，是被包容地看见
    </div>
    <div class="footprints" style="margin-top: 48px;">
      <div class="footprint"></div>
      <div class="footprint"></div>
      <div class="footprint"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>

</body>
</html>
